    "description": "Download Lotus Chess here! https://onelink.to/lotus-agadmator \nSearch all my videos easy https://agadmator-library.github.io/\nThumbnail photos by Lennart Ootes https://x.com/LennartOotes\n\n0:00 Hello Everyone!\n00:20 Game Starts!\n01:45 Completely New Game!\n06:32 It Was In This Position\n08:30 Legends of the Channel\n\nCaruana, Fabiano (2784) - Firouzja, Alireza (2766)\nGrand Chess Tour: Sinquefield Cup 2025 (Chess.com) [03] 2025.08.20\nE21 Nimzo-Indian, three knights variation\n\n1.d4 Nf6 2.c4 e6 3.Nc3 Bb4 4.Nf3 b6 5.Bd2 Bb7 6.g3 Bxc3 7.Bxc3 Ne4 8.Rc1 d6 9.Bg2 O-O 10.O-O Nd7 11.d5 Nxc3 12.Rxc3 e5 13.e4 a5 14.Nd2 c6 15.Re1 cxd5 16.cxd5 Nc5 17.Qe2 f5 18.exf5 Rxf5 19.Ne4 Qe7 20.Qb5 Qc7 21.b3 Raf8 22.a3 Qd8 23.Nxc5 dxc5 24.Rc2 Qd6 25.Rd2 Kh8 26.Be4 R5f6 27.Bg2 Rf5 28.Re3 h6 29.a4 Qf6 30.Ree2 Qd6 31.h4 R5f6 32.Qd3 Bc8 33.Qe4 Ba6 34.Re3 c4 35.bxc4 Qb4 36.Qc2 Qxc4 37.Qxc4 Bxc4 38.d6 Rd8 39.d7 Kg8 40.Rxe5 Kf7 41.Rd4 Ba2 42.Re2 Bb3 43.Re3 Ba2 44.Bf1 Kf8 45.Bb5 Re6 46.Rd2\n\nCheck out agadmator's merch here https://teespring.com/stores/agadmators-swag-store\nhttps://teespring.com/design-with-a-story-tm\n\nMailbox where you can send stuff:\n\nAntonio Radić\nAGADMATOR d.o.o.\nFranje Tuđmana 12\nCroatia\n48260 Križevci \np.s. this is not my home address :)\n\nContact me: agadmator@gmail.com \n\nVideo created by OBS\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nIf you realllly enjoy my content, you're welcome to support me and my channel with a small donation via PayPal or Crypto.\n\nLink to PayPal donation https://www.paypal.me/agadmator\n\nMaiar Wallet @agadmator or join me here https://get.maiar.com/referral/pv0mam6l2a\nBTC address bc1qckd3ut0hqyymzv33eus97ld8klj02xhk2kcwld\nBCH address qzmfclyn69hqhjslls40r7r0dsttwe3tcsl946w4fr\nLTC address Laarf1RmvCpLt2BcSwC1PBLG3hRC4HjBrz\nNANO nano_1h1kgfaq88t1btwadqzx73rbha5hwbb88sxmfns851kwj8hnosdj51w388xx\nMonero 4Adv